3. 養聲

廣東話：佢係一個專業歌手，每個星期都會去養聲。
English: He is a professional singer and goes to do vocal training every week.

4. 票尾

廣東話：我搵到個舊票尾，係個好嘅紀念品。
English: I found an old ticket stub, it's a good souvenir.

5. hacker

廣東話：佢係個黑客，可以輕鬆搵到網上嘅秘密資料。
English: He is a hacker and can easily find secret data on the internet.

6. 石斛蘭

廣東話：佢屋企後園種咗好多石斛蘭，好靚嘅。
English: He has many orchids growing in his backyard, they are very pretty.

7. 吊詭 (矛盾、悖論)

廣東話：呢個問題係個吊詭，冇法解答。
English: This question is a paradox, it cannot be answered.

8. 吊詭 (似非而是、荒謬)

廣東話：佢講嘅話係個吊詭，聽咗都唔明白。
English: What he said is absurd, I don't understand it.

9. 各為其主

廣東話：佢哋係各為其主，所以唔會合作。
English: They are each serving their own masters, so they won't cooperate.

10. 軸蓋

廣東話：車嘅軸蓋搗落咗，要緊急處理。
English: The car's hubcap fell off, it needs urgent attention.

11. 打哥夫

廣東話：周末同朋友去打哥夫，真係開心。
English: I went golfing with friends over the weekend, it was really fun.

12. 免揀

廣東話：呢間店嘅貨品係免揀嘅，買咗就係咁。
English: The products in this store are non-selectable, what you buy is what you get.

13. 擺闊佬

廣東話：佢仲係個新移民，仲未學會擺闊佬。
English: He is still a new immigrant and hasn't learned how to show off.

14. 廣播劇

廣東話：我每晚都會收聽廣播劇，聽緊好入嘅故事。
English: I listen to radio dramas every night, I enjoy the stories.

15. 錄影機

廣東話：我買咗部新錄影機，準備搵個好嘅角度搵影。
English: I bought a new camera, I'm going to find a good angle to shoot.

16. 吟詩吟唔甩

廣東話：佢講嘅係真係吟詩吟唔甩嘅證據。
English: What he said is irrefutable evidence.

17. 佈道大會

廣東話：呢個禮拜日有佈道大會，好多人都會去。
English: There is a preaching conference this Sunday, many people will go.

